Ranger Help for: set snare
===========================

SYNTAX:      snare
USAGE:       forest,plains,swamp,desert,jungle,hills,road,beach,
             underground,mountain,arctic,barren
SLOT COST:   9
BASE SP:     35
SKILL TYPE:  defensive

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to set up a hidden snare trap in the
surrounding terrain. Players or NPCs that are in the room when the
snare is set cannot be caught in it, since they are aware of its
presence. The first creature that wanders into the room will be
caught. Rangers, being adept at reading the wild, can spot and avoid
snare traps set by other Rangers. How long a victim remains snared
depends on how proficient the Ranger is at making them.
